13 November 2014Minister of Communications, Ms Faith Muthambi, will today answer Oral Questions in the National Council of Provinces.The questions are part of the Economic Cluster 4 and replies will focus on amongst others media independence and performance management of staff.Date: Thursday, 13 November 2014 Time: 14h00 Venue: NCOP, ParliamentEnquiries: Ayanda Holo Cell: 061 488 0634Issued by Department of Communications